  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>ABS MBS Positions</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio9e30c753b1081d4be10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">ABS MBS Positions </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> The report provides data on <a class=\"xref\" href=\"950f6551c939d51be10000000a445394.html\">Asset-Backed Securities and Mortgage-Backed Securities</a> positions\nincluding cumulative repayments and the original nominal amount. </p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Integration\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Integration</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> This report is a query. It is based onInfoSet\n<span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">/SAPQUERY/CFM_ABSMBS_POS</span>, which in turn, is based\non logical database <span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">FTI_TR_POSITIONS</span>. </p>\n<p class=\"p\"> The technical name of the query is <span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">CFM_POS_14</span>. </p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Features\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Features</h2>\n\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Selection</span>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"loio9e30c753b1081d4be10000000a174cb4__ul_x4b_hhv_4bb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"b6fac5536a51204be10000000a174cb4.html\">Product Groups</a>\n</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"ddfac5536a51204be10000000a174cb4.html\">Selections</a>\n</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"adfac5536a51204be10000000a174cb4.html\">Control Parameters</a>\n</p></li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Output</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"> The list is displayed using the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">SAP List Viewer</span> . </p>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">See also:</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"4dd40b7ac2234be2e10000000a42189c.html\" title=\"\">SAP List Viewer for SAP GUI (Classic)</a>\n</p>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
